com.revature.jfbennatt.ers.controller.delegates

Class SubmitReimbursementDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revature.jfbennatt.ers.controller.delegates.Delegate
      • com.revature.jfbennatt.ers.controller.delegates.SubmitReimbursementDelegate

  • public class SubmitReimbursementDelegate
extends Delegate
    This class handles reimbursement submissions. This class needs to be declared (i.e. should not be declared as a Delegate object). This is because this class needs the RequestDispatcher to communicate success (or failure) to the ViewDelegate.
    Author:
    Jared F Bennatt
